*Flujo: Cambio de texto*
--
1. MDDocumentLineEditor._on_text_changed(new_text)
2. → operations.update_line_text(index, new_text)
3. → state_manager.update_line_text(index, text)
4. → md_line.md_text = text (actualiza MDLine)
5. → md_line.update_type() (detecta nuevo tipo)</panel_attributes>
    <additional_attributes/>
  </element>
  <element>
    <id>UMLNote</id>
    <coordinates>
      <x>0</x>
      <y>1470</y>
      <w>420</w>
      <h>180</h>
    </coordinates>
    <panel_attributes>bg=#CCFFCC
*Flujo: Filtrar por texto*
--
1. InputSearchOrFilter.filter_toggle → state='toggled'
2. → App._on_filter_state_change(instance, state)
3. → operations.filter_by_text(text, include_parents)
4. → Para cada línea:
      - coincide: state_manager.set_visibility(index, True)
      - no coincide: state_manager.set_visibility(index, False)
5. → state_manager._emit_event(LineStateEvent)
6. → MDDocumentLineEditor._on_line_state_changed()
7. → widget.visible = line_state.visible</panel_attributes>
    <additional_attributes/>
  </element>
  <element>
    <id>UMLNote</id>
    <coordinates>
      <x>460</x>
      <y>1480</y>
      <w>420</w>
      <h>170</h>
    </coordinates>
    <panel_attributes>bg=#CCFFCC
*Flujo: Limpiar filtro*
--
1. InputSearchOrFilter.filter_toggle → state='untoggled'
2. → App._on_filter_state_change(instance, state)
3. → operations.clear_filter()
4. → Para cada línea: state_manager.set_visibility(index, True)
5. → state_manager._emit_event(LineStateEvent)
6. → MDDocumentLineEditor._on_line_state_changed()
7. → widget.visible = True (muestra todos)</panel_attributes>
    <additional_attributes/>
  </element>
  <element>
    <id>UMLNote</id>
    <coordinates>
      <x>0</x>
      <y>1680</y>
      <w>420</w>
      <h>200</h>
    </coordinates>
    <panel_attributes>bg=#CCFFCC
*Flujo: Búsqueda (navegar a coincidencia)*
--
1. InputSearchOrFilter.search_button → on_click
2. → dispatch('on_search', text)
3. → App._on_search_event(instance, text)
4. → operations.search_and_navigate(text, direction=1)
   a. Buscar siguiente línea con text desde active_index
   b. state_manager.activate_line(found_index)
   c. MDDocumentEditor.scroll_to_index(found_index)
5. → state_manager._emit_event(LineStateEvent)
6. → MDDocumentLineEditor._on_line_state_changed()
7. → widget activa + scroll visible</panel_attributes>
    <additional_attributes/>
  </element>
